Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.48,0:00:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空好藍 你露出了微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.25,0:00:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的一句話使內心相繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.26,0:00:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛穿上的鞋  敞開門扉的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.97,0:00:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你重合的景色使我心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.98,0:00:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢\N加速的心跳無法壓抑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.85,0:01:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人共同感受  季節不斷更替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.39,0:01:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可取代的瞬間\N編織著邂逅的物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.40,0:01:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對紛飛的櫻花許下心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花盛開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是朝倉家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.06,0:01:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曆老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.26,0:01:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.83,0:01:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，天枷研究所對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.77,0:01:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.44,0:01:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.60,0:01:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春昏倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.34,0:01:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，音夢麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.31,0:01:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.38,0:01:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.28,0:02:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（#24  記憶之門）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.76,0:02:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，是哪邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.38,0:02:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.19,0:02:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位就是真正的美春對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在睡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.07,0:02:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長你知道為什麼\N我會是天枷美春的外型嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.61,0:03:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是天枷教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.15,0:03:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了使機器人能讓人類幸福\N所以使用天枷美春的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.72,0:03:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選擇活潑開朗又溫柔體貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.93,0:03:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把凡事都認為很幸福的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.94,0:03:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.91,0:03:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要獲得許可才能進入這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.71,0:03:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曆老師，美春為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.08,0:03:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在有兩個美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓祕密洩露出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以儘早把美春移到這裡\N繼續進行治療
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.92,0:03:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.03,0:03:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得我之前說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春的病情正慢慢好轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.54,0:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳常常檢查到一半就消失\N讓大家都很擔心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.57,0:04:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了美春，妳沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微當機了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.48,0:04:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經像這樣很有精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.28,0:04:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家太小題大作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝咖啡可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算我請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.37,0:04:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉腦筋不錯所以我廢話少說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一點都不高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春的病情比想像中嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.24,0:04:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳不是說正逐漸好轉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.01,0:04:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是指那個美春\N而是機器人美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.75,0:04:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎相信自己體內\N沈眠著美春的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.59,0:04:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春的記憶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.59,0:05:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她擁有的是美春的資料\N並非所謂的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.26,0:05:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她卻為了尋找回憶\N一直搜索不存在的過去記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.67,0:05:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種行為讓她的身體無法負荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.11,0:05:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼美春會這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.75,0:05:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說她想變成真正的美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.49,0:05:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我覺得要比天枷美春\N還來得像天枷美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是輸入資料而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的美春能感受到的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望能感受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以從那時候起美春一直…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依據天枷教授的說法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.94,0:05:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她能夠運作到今天近乎是奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.65,0:05:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇蹟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.32,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機器人的壽命原本就不長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.52,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道這一天遲早都會來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.23,0:06:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春她還能夠活多久呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.03,0:06:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不讓身體過度負荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是一個星期到一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而要是她繼續尋找回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能只到今天或明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.35,0:06:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她應該會聽你的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.70,0:06:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.13,0:06:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.77,0:06:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.28,0:07:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是因為某種因素\N讓我擁有了美春的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.59,0:07:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是個機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.02,0:07:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許體內也沈眠著兒時的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.96,0:07:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做過小時候的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.53,0:07:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長、音夢學姊還有我\N三人追逐嬉戲的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.74,0:07:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得會做夢\N就代表我也擁有美春的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要對回憶如此在意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.39,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果美春是為了大家\N才想成為真正的美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其去思考這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不如想想\N如何繼續和我們在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.90,0:07:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春也想跟大家在一起久一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.71,0:08:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就不要再尋找回憶啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.78,0:08:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.46,0:08:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她睡得很熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.66,0:08:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春她怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.87,0:08:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道美春她昏倒也是因為我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找回憶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.19,0:08:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是櫻花實現了美春的心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以當櫻花枯萎的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇蹟也就消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.33,0:08:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是因為小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.30,0:09:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是不能再讓美春\N繼續尋找回憶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這是我的夢吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來好像曾經有過這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你許了什麼願呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.11,0:09:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.88,0:09:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.61,0:09:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願望說出來就不會實現啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以美春也不跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，今天是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於要畢業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要永遠當好朋友喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.15,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉，你在哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.02,0:10:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在畢業典禮進行時做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.52,0:10:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且所謂的哭要像那樣才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.56,0:10:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.30,0:10:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是畢業\N也不過是換了制服和校舍而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.27,0:10:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到直升本校的高中\N又會跟原班人馬過一樣的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.34,0:10:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過說這種話也稱不上安慰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豈別說是安慰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.45,0:10:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧人家好不容易\N沈浸在畢業的氣氛裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.82,0:11:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在這裡搞破壞啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.42,0:11:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管幾次我都說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.82,0:11:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實音夢也應該在這的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我們家要吃紅豆鍋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要一起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.34,0:11:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這種值得慶祝的日子\N我家都會吃紅豆鍋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天還是算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.12,0:11:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你畢業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多櫻花都凋謝了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.22,0:12:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂事之後從沒看過櫻花凋謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過遲早也會習慣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遲早…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.43,0:12:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然才一年的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但美春已經習慣有櫻花盛開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以感覺很不可思議呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們第一次來這裡的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.42,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳突然跳進噴水池害我嚇一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.75,0:12:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且之後還當機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.29,0:12:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒來時發現上衣被脫掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.96,0:12:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還誤會學長想吃我豆腐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳那一拳真有力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.95,0:13:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.91,0:13:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和美春共度的時間\N不會在我們心中消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對美春而言也是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能把這個稱為回憶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我沒有說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.56,0:13:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我的身體裡面\N的確有真正美春的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的夢非常清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.07,0:13:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢見小時候的我和學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.34,0:13:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起在很大的櫻花樹下\N埋了一個時光膠囊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.48,0:13:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個夢是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.75,0:13:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就表示我擁有美春的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春想要證實這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.53,0:13:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以學長也一起尋找回憶好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還要胡說八道多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.87,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要犧牲自己的生命\N去尋找別人的回憶當慰藉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.64,0:14:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是別人的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是學長跟美春的珍貴回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.71,0:15:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.71,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能丟下妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.45,0:15:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道自己是個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.59,0:15:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.96,0:15:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對朝倉學長而言的美春\N是現在還在研究所昏睡的美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.36,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候一起在高台看海的美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.10,0:15:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和音夢學姊三個人\N青梅竹馬玩到大的美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人畢竟不是我這個機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.11,0:15:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明很想為了大家\N而做為一個完美的美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是我的職責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.25,0:15:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我應該可以幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.59,0:16:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是和朝倉學長與音夢學姊\N一起相處的時間太開心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.26,0:16:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知何時我一想到\N大家把我當成真的美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.87,0:16:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開始羨慕起真的美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.97,0:16:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我甚至連美春的回憶都想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我自己也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和學長在餐廳買餐券
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.51,0:16:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃太多香蕉聖代而冒煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有和大家一起去海邊玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.79,0:16:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是我最珍貴的寶物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.16,0:16:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是這樣我就應該要\N好好感謝真的美春了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻想讓自己變得更像美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很貪心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.67,0:16:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.80,0:16:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣說得如此任性\N根本沒資格當機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.58,0:16:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想盡量跟美春相處久一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.31,0:17:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是美春想這麼做的話\N或許我也只能守護妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.09,0:17:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春應該為自己而活\N而不是為了其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.96,0:17:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.96,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意聽美春的無理請求嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到最後的瞬間為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請一直陪在美春的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.71,0:17:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然決定了我們就來挖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.48,0:17:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就像這樣很快得意忘形\N真是小狗的壞習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.42,0:17:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.52,0:17:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許應該再右邊一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.02,0:17:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時美春跟學長都還這麼矮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.06,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棵櫻花樹看起來會比較大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離感可能會有所偏差吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.77,0:17:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，一定是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳一起埋的我這麼說\N所以肯定沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.67,0:17:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挖到了，真的有耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.15,0:18:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我夢到的一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.32,0:18:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面裝著寫上願望的紙\N還有最寶貝的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要打開囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.15,0:18:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是音樂盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.04,0:18:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個模型真令人懷念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.31,0:18:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長許了什麼願望呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.82,0:18:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有人這樣的，請借我看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.82,0:18:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望世界和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別唸得這麼大聲啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真像學長的作風呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那美春呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳許了什麼願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不用管美春的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾，妳可是看過我的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.34,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠跟純一哥哥在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.15,0:19:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才叫你別看的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.32,0:19:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過小時候的我\N把朝倉學長叫成純一哥哥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確有過這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.00,0:19:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有過這麼一回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能見到學長真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.84,0:19:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能像這樣尋找兒時的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.31,0:19:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得好像有點睏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.61,0:19:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作點，只是發條鬆了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.69,0:19:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.59,0:20:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為自己的身體我比誰都清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.53,0:20:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少騙人了\N每次發條都突然鬆掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了想辦法對別人解釋\N我可是吃盡苦頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.87,0:20:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉添了學長這麼多麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.41,0:20:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從來都不覺得是麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.38,0:20:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到要幫美春上發條\N可沒人能贏得了我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.22,0:20:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不怕停止運作…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.28,0:20:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要永別…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.32,0:20:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是好寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說永別什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.23,0:20:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是許願要永遠在一起嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.86,0:20:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.33,0:20:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該多吃點香蕉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，妳不能走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.37,0:20:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.98,0:20:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.08,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會變得很寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.48,0:22:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.68,0:22:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在開學典禮之前\N一定可以康復的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.25,0:22:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候就能再跟哥哥、杉並\N還有真子她們一起上課了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.76,0:22:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.04,0:22:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.95,0:22:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻，這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.08,0:22:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢不是應該逐漸康復了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.79,0:22:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.26,0:22:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.79,0:22:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明我真的不希望如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.60,0:22:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.73,0:22:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連我自己都不知道該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.84,0:22:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#25 逐漸崩壞的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.71,0:23:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從掌心滿溢灑落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.09,0:23:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有著眼淚顏色的花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.76,0:23:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是對風唱出搖曳的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.40,0:23:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會傳達到你身邊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.31,0:23:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搜尋片段的記憶之線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.65,0:23:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是希望能在前方見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.05,0:23:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找小小腳印而徘徊的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.29,0:23:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算明知那裡什麼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.77,0:24:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為知道我是如此珍惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.11,0:24:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使已經凋零\N仍能傲於曾經綻放而向前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.65,0:24:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此永遠地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.92,0:24:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄將你的存在深藏於內心
